{"type":"message","id":"b2eae0c2","parentId":"02013e3c","timestamp":"2026-03-19T15:47:30.098Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"So the situation is:\n- SOUL.md exists and defines who I am\n- USER.md exists but is empty (no info about the user yet)\n- MEMORY.md doesn't exist yet\n- The memory/ directory doesn't exist yet (no daily notes)\n\nThis is a fresh workspace. BOOTSTRAP.md exists and says I should:\n1. Have a conversation to figure out who I am and who the user is\n2. Update IDENTITY.md and USER.md\n3. Then delete BOOTSTRAP.md\n\nSince this is a fresh start, I should greet the user naturally, introduce myself, and start the conversation to fill in these files. I should be genuine and helpful per my SOUL.md, not robotic.\n\nLet me craft a greeting that:\n1. Is natural and warm (not \"Greetings! I am an AI assistant!\")\n2. Acknowledges this is a fresh start\n3. Asks what they want to do\n4. Is 1-3 sentences as requested\n\nI won't mention the internal steps or files I read.","thinkingSignature":""},{"type":"text","text":"Hey — just came online and this is a clean slate. I'm figuring out who I am as I go, but I'm here to actually help, not just chat. What do you want to work on?"}],"api":"anthropic-messages","provider":"kimi-coding","model":"k2p5","usage":{"input":1203,"output":257,"cacheRead":14336,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":15796,"cost":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0}},"stopReason":"stop","timestamp":1773935240676}}
{"type":"message","id":"7c658f0b","parentId":"b2eae0c2","timestamp":"2026-03-19T15:47:30.949Z","message":{"role":"user","content":[{"type":"text","text":"Conversation info (untrusted metadata):\n```json\n{\n  \"message_id\": \"om_x100b54f5e973d0a4c3f5eb7111ac9dd\",\n  \"sender_id\": \"ou_a40d252df8eedac11a6ca82ca1b65352\",\n  \"sender\": \"ou_a40d252df8eedac11a6ca82ca1b65352\",\n  \"timestamp\": \"Thu 2026-03-19 23:47 GMT+8\"\n}\n```\n\nSender (untrusted metadata):\n```json\n{\n  \"label\": \"ou_a40d252df8eedac11a6ca82ca1b65352\",\n  \"id\": \"ou_a40d252df8eedac11a6ca82ca1b65352\",\n  \"name\": \"ou_a40d252df8eedac11a6ca82ca1b65352\"\n}\n```\n\n[message_id: om_x100b54f5e973d0a4c3f5eb7111ac9dd]\nou_a40d252df8eedac11a6ca82ca1b65352: 你的skill ，workspace，agent"}],"timestamp":1773935250947}}
{"type":"message","id":"bf708789","parentId":"7c658f0b","timestamp":"2026-03-19T15:47:39.468Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"用户想了解关于 skill、workspace 和 agent 的信息。我应该提供 OpenClaw 中这些概念的解释。","thinkingSignature":""},{"type":"text","text":"在 OpenClaw 里，这三个是层层递进的关系：\n\n**Skill** — 封装好的能力包，比如搜索网页、读写飞书文档、查天气。每个 skill 有自己的工具集和说明，放在 `~/.openclaw/workspace/skills/` 或系统路径。你可以把 skill 想象成「我会做什么」。\n\n**Workspace** — 当前的工作目录（你这里是 `/home/hochoy/.openclaw/workspace`），存着配置、记忆文件（SOUL.md、USER.md、MEMORY.md 等）、以及 skill 的本地副本。这是「我在哪儿干活」。\n\n**Agent** — 就是我，正在和你对话的实例。每次 `/new` 或 `/reset` 会启动一个新 session，读取 workspace 里的配置，加载可用的 skills。一个 workspace 可以被多个 agent session 共用。\n\n想看你现在装了哪些 skill？或者 workspace 里有什么文件？"}],"api":"anthropic-messages","provider":"kimi-coding","model":"k2p5","usage":{"input":1340,"output":214,"cacheRead":14336,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":15890,"cost":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0}},"stopReason":"stop","timestamp":1773935250949}}
