{"type":"message","id":"5c2e0d27","parentId":"40d5a475","timestamp":"2026-03-19T15:50:13.976Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"现在我已经收集了足够的信息来回答用户关于三个 agent（main、demo、wechat-assistant）的权限对比。让我再查看一下 openclaw.json 的配置来了解具体的权限设置。","thinkingSignature":""},{"type":"toolCall","id":"tool_QsB6tsJYT7FL9s66GTjowi1H","name":"read","arguments":{"file_path":"/home/hochoy/.openclaw/openclaw.json"}}],"api":"anthropic-messages","provider":"kimi-coding","model":"k2p5","usage":{"input":9374,"output":68,"cacheRead":33024,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":42466,"cost":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0}},"stopReason":"toolUse","timestamp":1773935409727}}
{"type":"message","id":"747a00cf","parentId":"5c2e0d27","timestamp":"2026-03-19T15:50:13.982Z","message":{"role":"toolResult","toolCallId":"tool_QsB6tsJYT7FL9s66GTjowi1H","toolName":"read","content":[{"type":"text","text":"{\n  \"meta\": {\n    \"lastTouchedVersion\": \"2026.3.13\",\n    \"lastTouchedAt\": \"2026-03-18T06:33:42.088Z\"\n  },\n  \"wizard\": {\n    \"lastRunAt\": \"2026-03-18T06:33:25.317Z\",\n    \"lastRunVersion\": \"2026.3.13\",\n    \"lastRunCommand\": \"doctor\",\n    \"lastRunMode\": \"local\"\n  },\n  \"auth\": {\n    \"profiles\": {\n      \"kimi:default\": {\n        \"provider\": \"kimi\",\n        \"mode\": \"api_key\"\n      }\n    }\n  },\n  \"env\": { \n    \"KIMI_API_KEY\": \"sk-kimi-umzkSc1s95X5owMUIbZn3VLkBGZeiIWwWrQd7oBPYZcKKQ2IBafWm3NZvSugTNhe\" \n  },\n  \"agents\": {\n    \"defaults\": {\n      \"model\": {\n        \"primary\": \"kimi-coding/k2p5\"\n      },\n      \"models\": {\n        \"kimi-coding/k2p5\": { \n          \"alias\": \"Kimi K2.5\" \n        }\n      },\n      \"workspace\": \"/home/hochoy/.openclaw/workspace\",\n      \"sandbox\": {\n        \"mode\": \"off\"\n      }\n    },\n    \"list\": [\n      {\n        \"id\": \"main\",\n        \"model\": \"kimi-coding/k2p5\"\n      },\n      {\n        \"id\": \"demo\",\n        \"name\": \"demo\",\n        \"workspace\": \"/home/hochoy/.openclaw/workspace-demo\",\n        \"agentDir\": \"/home/hochoy/.openclaw/agents/demo/agent\",\n        \"model\": \"kimi-coding/k2p5\"\n      },\n      {\n        \"id\": \"wechat-assistant\",\n        \"name\": \"wechat-assistant\",\n        \"workspace\": \"/home/hochoy/.openclaw/workspace-wechat-assistant\",\n        \"agentDir\": \"/home/hochoy/.openclaw/agents/wechat-assistant/agent\",\n        \"model\": \"kimi-coding/k2p5\"\n      }\n    ]\n  },\n  \"tools\": {\n    \"profile\": \"full\",\n    \"web\": {\n      \"search\": {\n        \"provider\": \"brave\"\n      }\n    },\n    \"allow\": [\"*\"],\n    \"exec\": {\n      \"host